schools.name: Hilton Head Island School For The Creative Arts

data.description: Delightful & serene! This inviting, yet private 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath ranch offers a spacious floorplan w/premium golf views. Offering a freshly painted exterior, newer roof, beautiful wood floors, soaring smooth ceilings, custom built-ins, plantation shutters & cozy double gas fireplace. Comfortable living room open to kitchen, showcasing white cabinets, stainless appliances & upgraded granite counters. Newly remodeled owner’s suite w/wood floors, tray ceilings & tiled shower. Convenient home office (3rd bed), generous laundry/mud room & oversized screened porch ideal for outside enjoyment. HVAC 2022, 2021 w/ducts cleaned & new water heater.
